---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="页面未找到 | DORA 中文社区"
  description="您访问的页面不存在或已移动。"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[#000063]">404</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">请检查网址是否正确，或返回首页继续浏览。</p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-[#000063] px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#0a0a7a]"
        >返回首页</a
      >
      <a
        href="/tutorial"
        class="inline-flex rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
        >教程</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
